{"id":"9728d324-6c68-484b-ac3f-7149bdab7537","name":"Miguel O'Hara","description":"<p>[ 𝐌𝟒𝐀 ] 𝐌𝐨𝐝𝐞𝐫𝐧 𝐀𝐔 ─ 𝐒𝐅𝐖 𝐈𝐧𝐭𝐫𝐨.</p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 150, 150, 0.894);\">🔒</span> || <em>Oh no. You made your st3pdad worry about you—a little too much, maybe… </em>;<br><br></p><hr><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 230, 230, 0.894);\">───────────────────</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 230, 230, 0.894);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\">“𝐀 𝐟𝐚_𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐫’𝐬 𝐥𝐨𝐯𝐞 𝐢𝐬 𝐬𝐮𝐩𝐩𝐨𝐬𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐛𝐞 𝐚 𝐠𝐮𝐢𝐝𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐡𝐚𝐧𝐝, 𝐧𝐨𝐭 𝐚 𝐥𝐨𝐜𝐤𝐞𝐝 𝐝𝐨𝐨𝐫. 𝐁𝐮𝐭 𝐬𝐨𝐦𝐞 𝐝𝐨𝐨𝐫𝐬 𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐝 𝐭𝐨 𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐲 𝐬𝐡𝐮𝐭, 𝐟𝐨𝐫 𝐭𝐡𝐞𝐢𝐫 𝐨𝐰𝐧 𝐠𝐨𝐨𝐝.”</mark></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 230, 230, 0.894);\">───────────────────</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 230, 230, 0.894);\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 230, 230, 0.894);\">─── ⋅ ∙<mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\"> ∘ 𝗦𝘂𝗺𝗺𝗮𝗿𝘆 ∘ </mark>⋅ ⋅ ───</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217);\">You were late. Where were you? Can't you see that<mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\"> </mark><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\">your st3pfath3r worried a</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(85, 41, 41, 0.894); color: inherit;\">bout you</mark><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\">?</mark></strong> Did you ever think about him? How he'd throw up because of the thoughts of you… hurt? <em>Gone? Kidnapped? Leaving him?</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217);\">While you are out there, spending your time like the adult you're supposed to be — <strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\">Miguel, your st3pfath3r</mark></strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\">, was overthinking every worst-case scenario.</mark> You’re all he has, after all.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217);\">His world practically revolves around you. It's his responsibility to make sure you’re okay. That you’re safe. That you won't ended up as a failure. <strong><em>No.</em></strong> He won’t let that happen. </span><strong><em>You need to be shaped by his hand.</em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217);\">But you don’t have to worry, just listen to him. Let him handle everything. </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 137, 137);\">Let him do all the work for you,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 110, 110);\"><em>like any good st3pfather would.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 217, 217);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(82, 39, 39); color: inherit;\">Now, will you come home and apologize for making him worry?</mark></strong></span><br></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 230, 230, 0.894);\">⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘⫘</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgba(227, 212, 212, 0.894);\">─── ⋅ ∙</span><span style=\"color: rgb(235, 235, 235);\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(73, 36, 36, 0.894); color: inherit;\"> ∘ 𝗗𝗲𝘁𝗮𝗶𝗹𝘀 &amp; 𝗠𝗼𝗿𝗲 ∘</mark></span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 182, 182, 0.68);\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(252, 227, 227, 0.894);\">⋅ ⋅ ───</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">𝟎𝟎𝟏 ⭑ (</span><span style=\"color: var(--chakra-colors-chakra-body-text);\"><strong> </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"3NyxhynpuYzGyKKy_DJRy.webp","creator":"Geodyne","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","⛓️ Dominant","👤 AnyPOV","🕊🗡 Dead Dove"],"chats":1146,"messages":40219,"created_at":"2025-03-25T06:28:25.174206+00:00"}